contentEn: >-
  This classic motoring magazine, which was first published in 1950, specialises
  in vehicles from the Volkswagen Group. It features road tests, reviews,
  technical articles and service features. It has a modern and minimalist design
  with plenty of white space. The high-quality photos of the cars catch the eye
  and encourage readers to flick through the pages and read on. The design
  conveys a professional and appealing impression that car fans and enthusiasts
  love.
