        en: >-
          For the new Audi RS3, we handled both the car photography and the
          layout design. To make the page a little more engaging, we used
          close-ups of the seat upholstery, overlaid with an image of the car.
          The text was also laid out in two columns for easy readability,
          creating a certain structure within the layout.
